s the collapse on small scales.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Oct 2015 19:53:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Feb 2016 15:41:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-17"}
